    "Id": 4,
    "Content": "```js\nimport UibookCase from 'uibook/case'\nimport Button from '../src/button'\n\nexport default {\n  component: Button,\n  cases: [\n    () => <UibookCase>Button</UibookCase>,\n    () => <UibookCase props={{ isSmall: true }}>Small button</UibookCase>\n  ]\n}\n```",
